My problem is that my lower lip is bigger than my upper lip. Some people suggested that if I keep licking it, it will reduce in size. I tried this but it didn’t work. Is there any drug or special treatment for this? Please help because I am ashamed of my appearance. Haruna (by SMS)  When an unevenness of the lips is very slight or minimal, it can be corrected by practicing facial exercises. However, since you have tried this technique and it has failed, you have to consider lip reconstruction. This is a procedure usually performed by a plastic surgeon who can be contacted at the nearest specialist or teaching hospital to you. Lip surgeries are done with both a functional and aesthetic focus in mind. Sometimes additional skin must be removed from other places on your body to reconstruct the lips.   YOU SHOULD NOT MISS THESE HEADLINES FROM NIGERIAN TRIBUNE FLICKERS: Nigerian Army: Timelines Of Lies And A Million Skulls In Ogun’s Shrine
